@mainpage Stackdriver Debugger API C++ Client Library

An idiomatic C++ client library for the [Stackdriver Debugger
API][cloud-service-docs], a service to examine the call stack and variables of
a running application without stopping or slowing it down.

While this library is **GA**, please note Google Cloud C++ client libraries do **not** follow [Semantic Versioning](https://semver.org/).

